purpose:
  - Family共有時の共同編集挙動を設計する
  - owner / family_editor / family_viewer の変更反映ルールを整理する
  - 編集衝突や owner確認が必要な場面を明確にする

runtime_principles:
  - owner is final decision maker
  - family_editor can help edit within scope
  - family_viewer is read-only
  - no silent override for major changes
  - long-term planning context should be preserved
